## Limitations
The report is based on available online sources and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. The findings are limited to the scope of the sources reviewed, and further research could provide additional insights. Additionally, the complexity of the self as a construct means that new theories and research findings continue to emerge, which may not be fully captured in this report.